## ğŸš€ Deployment

### Backend (Render)

* Connect your GitHub repo to Render.
* Use the `render.yaml` file for automatic deployment.
* Add environment variables in Render dashboard under the Environment tab.

### Frontend (Vercel)

* Import the `frontend/` folder on Vercel.
* Set `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE` to your Render backend URL.

